{"tid":1419023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將中國列為匯率操縱國","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T23:52:37.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67bd347f71dfed76260ff408d4d2d897dc09e063","tid":1419023,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1472962_1_20190806063240.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1472962_1_20190806063240.jpg&h=d338161d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人民幣匯率自2008年來，首度跌穿七算的心理關口後，美國財政部正式將中國列為匯率操縱國。<br />\n<br />\n財政部發表聲明，批評中國在中美貿易戰升溫時，削弱人民幣匯率，財長努欽在總統特朗普的支持下，確認中國為匯率操縱國，努欽將與國際貨幣基金組織商討，消除中國最新行動帶來的不公平競爭優勢。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前在社交網站貼文，指中國讓他們的貨幣貶值到歷史低位，這些叫「操縱匯率」，是嚴重違規。<br />\n<br />\n人民銀行行長易綱說，8月以來很多貨幣兌美元貶值，人民幣匯率亦受一定程度影響，波動是市場驅動及決定，強調中國堅持市場決定的匯率制度，不搞競爭性貶值，不將匯率用於競爭目的，亦不會將匯率作為應對貿易爭端等的工具。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472962-20190806.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472962-20190806.htm&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=78cd6f0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472962-20190806.htm&h=59149c16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472962-20190806.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a237a6b54923dc350ca27504dfa4ea7d548e006b","tid":1419023,"uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:52:37.000Z","msg":"快d全面收支那貨45%關税<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}